snippet.title: DreadHaunt |  Southeast Asia Games Onward 2024 Cut Trailer
snippet.description:
Set on a forsaken island off Jakarta’s northern coast, a place steeped in arcane energy and unsolved mysteries, you will face anomalous entities, cursed objects, and strange phenomena that modern science cannot explain.
As a member of a covert containment agency comprising scientists, exorcists, and believers your mission is to locate and secure cursed items believed to fuel the island's paranormal activity. 

Twitter : x.com/dh_games
More about the game : store.steampowered.com/app/1855580/DreadHaunt/
